data.value:
My topic is about my cats Chester and Ritz.
On October 24 2020 I got Chester and Ritz from the SPCA. They are brothers so I felt like I couldn't seperate them.
Chester is very timid and Ritz super energetic and nosey. They like to sleep all day and play all night.
I love them a lot.
